snippet.title: Westley Nelson
snippet.description:
I am Heliotrope Journey's Creative Director and Marketing Liaison and hold a bachelor's degree in art & art history from Eastern Connecticut State University.

My greatest wish is to convert Heliotrope Journey to a franchise on top of inspiring my fellow team members and the less fortunate to reach for the stars. Come say hi. :)

P.S.: I also chat with actors I either recognize from my childhood or stream Bloodstained: Ritual of the Night to get me to crawl out of my shell. Whatever helps makes life worth living.

Avatar Illustrated by GT Classic Avatars

Header Photo by Alexander Bobrov from Pexels
